Title: Dana Carvey: Straight White Male, 60
Actors: Dana Carvey, Dex Carvey, Thomas Carvey
Plot: Emmy-winning comedian Dana Carvey blends pitch-perfect takes on so-true-it-hurts stories from his life as a dad of millenials. Add in teenagers, chinese factory workers, and hitler; this is one "SNL" star you can count on to make a good impression.
